.Dd June 24, 2026
.Dt X11DND_SET_AWARE 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm x11dnd_set_aware
.Nd set the XdndAware property on a window
.Sh LIBRARY
.Lb libx11dnd
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In x11dnd.h
.Ft Bool
.Fn x11dnd_set_aware "Display *dpy" "Window win" "int version"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Fn x11dnd_set_aware
sets the
.Li XdndAware
property on
.Fa win
advertising XDnD protocol
.Fa version .
Use
.Dv X11DND_VERSION_5
for the current protocol version.
.Pp
This function is called internally by
.Xr x11dnd_register_target 3
and is rarely needed directly.
.Sh RETURN VALUES
Returns
.Dv True
on success,
.Dv False
on failure.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr x11dnd_register_target 3 ,
.Xr x11dnd_get_aware_version 3 ,
.Xr x11dnd 3
